        <ol>
            <li>Open a report.</li>
            <li>In the Report Editor, click the <span class="Emphasis">General</span> tab.</li>
            <li>In the <span class="Emphasis">Tables</span> field, scroll down to the <span class="Emphasis">Links</span> section.</li>
            <li>Click the <span class="Emphasis">Cross-Reference Suggestions</span> check box.</li>
            <li>
                <p>Click <span class="Emphasis">Generate</span>. The generated report will include cross-reference suggestions. </p>
                <p>
                    <img src="../../../../Images/Flare/Nav-Links/Xref-Suggestions-Report.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
                </p>
            </li>
